tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE parks (
    park_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    park_name TEXT,
    area_size FLOAT,
    location TEXT,
    open_hours TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE green_spaces (
  space_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  space_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  space_type VARCHAR(50),
  space_location VARCHAR(100),
  park_id INT,
  FOREIGN KEY (park_id) REFERENCES parks(park_id)
);

CREATE TABLE parks (
 id INT PRIMARY KEY,
 name VARCHAR(255),
 area FLOAT
)

CREATE TABLE green_spaces (
 id INT PRIMARY KEY,
 name VARCHAR(255),
 location VARCHAR(255)
)

CREATE TABLE park_visitors (
 id INT PRIMARY KEY,
 park_id INT,
 visitor_name VARCHAR(255)
)

CREATE TABLE park_ratings (
  rating_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  park_id INT,
  user_id INT,
  rating FLOAT NOT NULL,
  date_rated DATE
);

CREATE TABLE maintenance_records (
  record_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  park_id INT,
  maintenance_date DATE,
  maintenance_cost DECIMAL(10,2) NOT NULL,
  maintenance_notes TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE park_entrances (
  entrance_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  park_id INT NOT NULL,
  entrance_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  latitude DECIMAL(10, 8),
  longitude DECIMAL(11, 8)
);

CREATE TABLE park_reviews (
  review_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  park_id INT NOT NULL,
  visitor_id INT NOT NULL,
  rating INT,
  review_text TEXT
);
